snippet.title: So Much Stuff Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Sort through a different way to play hidden object games. Clear out various items and trinkets across many different environments to complete each level and enjoy a variety of tricky mini-games. So sit back, relax, and sort through it! There's so much stuff! 

Download the trial for your desktop!
PC: https://www.bigfishgames.com/us/en/games/15949/so-much-stuff-collectors-edition/?pc&lang=en
Mac: https://www.bigfishgames.com/us/en/games/15949/so-much-stuff-collectors-edition/?mac&lang=en

Available now!
